CHAT.comment: MT is about 30 minutes long. the tape is rather hard to understand. Fat and Chi are doing most of the talking , while Mot may be in the kitchen or elsewhere; after talking about the project a little , FAT and Chi talk about a movie Chi has seen. Chi describes why she liked <Honey I Blew Up the Kid> in a series of utterences beginning with <I like how>. Needless to say , the level of conversation is a little lower than expected for this family , but it's still a solid example of a family mealtime. For example , there's a negotiation over eating some salad before getting dessert. Yawn. I'd hoped for something more exciting.
